  "intermediate_belief": "If I can't manage my finances perfectly after the divorce, it means I'm failing at being independent and others will see me as incapable. I must not make mistakes or I'll prove that I can't handle life on my own. If I show I'm struggling, people will distance themselves even more.",
  "intermediate_belief_depression": "If I keep struggling with these financial problems, it just proves that things will never get better for me and I'm destined to be alone and overwhelmed.",
